OL,6,FNow the Criminal Cases Review
OL,7,FCommission, the body responsible for
OL,8,Finvestigating alleged miscarriages of
OL,9,Fjustice, has offered the unreserved
OL,10,Fapology after a review made it "clear
OL,11,F... that the commission failed" Mr
OL,12,FMalkinson.
OL,14,FBut Mr Malkinson branded the apology
OL,15,F"too little, too late" as he
OL,16,Fquestioned her sincerity and called on
OL,17,FJustice Secretary Alex Chalk to bring
OL,18,Fin "new leadership" at the CCRC.
