OL,6,FDuring his time in prison, Mr
OL,7,FMalkinson twice applied for his case
OL,8,Fto be referred for appeal by the
OL,9,FCriminal Cases Review Commission
OL,10,F(CCRC) but was turned down on both
OL,11,Foccasions.
OL,13,FHe had applied for his case to be
OL,14,Freviewed by the CCRC in 2009, but at
OL,15,Fthe conclusion of its review in 2012
OL,16,Fthe commission refused to order
OL,17,Ffurther forensic testing or refer the
OL,18,Fcase for appeal, amid concerns over
OL,19,Fcosts.
