OL,6,FA second application was rejected in
OL,7,F2020.
OL,9,FCrucial DNA evidence had been
OL,10,Favailable since 2007, but no match was
OL,11,Ffound on the police database at the
OL,12,Ftime.
OL,14,FMr Malkinson eventually had his 2003
OL,15,Fconviction quashed by the Court of
OL,16,FAppeal in July 2023 after new DNA
OL,17,Fevidence potentially linking another
OL,18,Fman to the crime was identified.
