OL,3,C'Unreserved apology' offered after
OL,4,Cwrongful rape conviction
OL,6,FThe chairwoman of the Criminal Cases
OL,7,FReview Commission (CCRC), Helen
OL,8,FPitcher, offered the "unreserved
OL,9,Fapology" after an independent review
OL,10,Fof the case by Chris Henley KC was
OL,11,Fcompleted.
OL,13,FMs Pitcher said: "Mr Henley's report
OL,14,Fmakes sobering reading, and it is
OL,15,Fclear from his findings that the
OL,16,Fcommission failed Andrew Malkinson.
OL,18,F"For this, I am deeply sorry. I have
OL,19,Fwritten to Mr Malkinson to offer him
OL,20,Fmy sincere regret and an unreserved
OL,21,Fapology on behalf of the commission.
