OL,6,FShe added that the organisation would
OL,7,Fprovide Mr Malkinson with a copy of
OL,8,Fthe review report, which contains nine
OL,9,Frecommendations, and that it intended
OL,10,Fto make the findings public at a later
OL,11,Fdate.
OL,13,FMr Malkinson, who previously called
OL,14,Ffor Ms Pitcher to be sacked and
OL,15,Fstripped of her OBE, said he felt
OL,16,F"vindicated" by the apology but it was
OL,17,F"too little, too late".
