OL,6,FHe said the CCRC's failings caused him
OL,7,Fa "world of pain" as he accused her of
OL,8,Fapologising now because "the CCRC has
OL,9,Fbeen found out, and the last escape
OL,10,Fhatch has now closed on them".
OL,12,FIn a statement issued on his behalf by
OL,13,Flegal charity Appeal, Mr Malkinson
OL,14,Fsaid: "The time for Helen Pitcher to
OL,15,Fapologise was last summer when I was
OL,16,Fexonerated.
