OL,3,C'Unreserved apology' offered after
OL,4,Cwrongful rape conviction
OL,6,F"It was already crystal clear that the
OL,7,FCCRC had completely failed me. Yet
OL,8,Fshe's held off on apologising until a
OL,9,Freport spelled this out for her in
OL,10,Fblack and white. It is hard for me to
OL,11,Fsee sincerity in an apology after all
OL,12,Fthis time.
OL,14,F"The CCRC's delay in apologising to me
OL,15,Fadded significantly to the mental
OL,16,Fturmoil I am experiencing as I
OL,17,Fcontinue to fight for accountability
OL,18,Ffor what was done to me."
