OL,6,FHe claimed Ms Pitcher disputed
OL,7,Fcriticisms of the CCRC's handling of
OL,8,Fhis case when they were put to her by
OL,9,Fhis lawyer in September last year and
OL,10,Frefused a direct request for an
OL,11,Fapology at the time.
OL,13,F"That smacks to me of someone who is
OL,14,Fin denial and not fit to lead a body
OL,15,Fwhich is meant to be dedicated to
OL,16,Frooting out failings in our justice
OL,17,Fsystem", he said, adding: "I hope the
OL,18,FJustice Secretary Alex Chalk will
OL,19,Fbring in new leadership at the CCRC.
