OL,6,F"I am innocent and I am not the only
OL,7,Fone. Others must not be let down as I
OL,8,Fwas. The CCRC should be led by people
OL,9,Fwith empathy, humility and a track
OL,10,Frecord of fighting injustice."
OL,12,FMr Malkinson's legal team previously
OL,13,Fdiscovered striking similarities
OL,14,Fbetween his ordeal and the earlier
OL,15,FCCRC case of Victor Nealon, whose 1997
OL,16,Fconviction was overturned by the Court
OL,17,Fof Appeal in December 2013 after new
OL,18,FDNA evidence was unearthed.
